import React from 'react'

const Navbar = () => {
  return (
    <nav className='navbar'>
      <NavLink
        to='/'
        className={({ isActive }) => (isActive ? 'link active' : 'link')}
      >
        Home
      </NavLink>
      <NavLink
        to='/about'
        className={({ isActive }) => (isActive ? 'link active' : 'link')}
      >
        About
      </NavLink>
      <NavLink
        to='/products'
        className={({ isActive }) => (isActive ? 'link active' : 'link')}
      >
        Products
      </NavLink>
    </nav>
  )
}

export default Navbar
